snippet: Spain’s Carlota Ciganda hit an eagle to level her match as Europe led the United States, 4-2, on the opening day of the Solheim Cup in St. Leon-Rot, Germany.
abstract: Europe leads United States, 4-2, in first round of Solheim Cup.
lead_paragraph: Spain’s Carlota Ciganda hit an eagle to level her match as Europe led the United States, 4-2, on the opening day of the Solheim Cup in St. Leon-Rot, Germany.
